Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.82,0:35:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  不該是這樣的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait, this isn't supposed to be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.04,0:35:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is not happening!
