Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.15,0:37:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-請原諒我  父親  -是我的錯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Please forgive me, father-- - It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.34,0:37:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我還沒有將你準備充分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't prepare you well enough.
