Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.58,0:37:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什么失誤可言  只有被浪費了的機會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are no mistakes, only opportunities wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.14,0:38:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事不會再發生了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It won't happen again.
