Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.39,0:38:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太神奇了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.83,0:38:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然他的大腦活動還沒完全恢復\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Brain activity isn't 100%,
