Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.61,0:38:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫  你還好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alan, are you OK?
